  <titles>
    <title as="introduced" type="short">Arsenic Reduction in Drinking Water Act</title>
    <title as="introduced" type="official">To amend the Safe Drinking Water Act to change the drinking water standard for arsenic from 50 parts per billion to 10 parts per billion by fiscal year 2003 and to 3 parts per billion by fiscal year 2006 and to authorize an $800 million to provide grants to small public drinking water systems to assist them in meeting these standards.</title>
